    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='153:179'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-1a' );" name="001-1a" class="pb">[001-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='179:187'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='187:208'>　詩故卷一　　　　　　　明　朱謀㙔　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='208:231'>周南者何岐周之風也詩六義有風雅頌而無南此何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='231:254'>　以稱南風之南也八風寒燠異徳升降殊情不為振</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='254:277'>　掉則為凄戾唯南風祥和鬯達長養萬物有豈樂而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='277:300'>　無怫鬱文王岐周之化實象之故不稱風而稱南也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='300:323'>　召公分陜矣何以稱南其化同也造王業之本莫如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='323:346'>　周南成王業之效莫如召南故大胥鼓南而鼓鐘以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='346:372'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-1b' );" name="001-1b" class="pb">[001-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='372:381'>　雅以南有㫖哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='381:404'>闗雎后妃之徳也何以言徳廣嬪御厚國本也國本莫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='404:427'>　重于嗣續婦徳莫難于不妬太姒能求庶女於窈窕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='427:450'>　側陋之間廣為則百斯男之地厥徳又何加焉雎鳩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='450:473'>　王雎亦謂之鶚大小如鴟深目目上骨露幽州名之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='473:496'>　曰鷲亦名白鷢不類鳬鷖也此鳥鷙而善漁每得隈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='496:519'>　潭隩渚輙盤飛雲際哀鳴求類而後下集焉非為其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='519:542'>　有别也窈窕猶言䆗窱謂窮巷深閨淑女之所在非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='542:568'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-2a' );" name="001-2a" class="pb">[001-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='568:591'>　幽閒貞静之説也荇菜葉紫莖白脆美可茹其葉始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='591:614'>　卷而漸開黄花六出今人不復采取第名之曰豬蓴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='614:637'>　闗雎一詩初非難説而毛韓齊魯各立異義良由辨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='637:660'>　物未明比興失所守師説者愈精愈逺愈索愈疎三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='660:674'>　百五篇用是不復得其故矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='674:697'>葛覃后妃之本也何以言本内教之所由立也太姒位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='697:720'>　乎正嫡廣求庶妾並處宫中不有所以教之得無安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='720:743'>　于怠荒乎蠶桑者后夫人之所有事而葛枲細務則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='743:769'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-2b' );" name="001-2b" class="pb">[001-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='769:792'>　庶婦之職也太姒身率絺綌服之無斁蠶桑可知矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='792:815'>　言告師氏太姒自寧其親也薄汚薄澣歸寧父母語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='815:838'>　庶妾也示之勤儉教之孝思非政本乎萋萋狀葛之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='838:861'>　始苗莫莫狀葛之成就莫莫云者誕節之謂非茂密</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='861:884'>　也私者親體之衵服衣則洩暑之常衣非燕服褘衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='884:890'>　之謂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='890:913'>卷耳后妃之志也何志乎志逺人也丈夫有事四方無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='913:936'>　所庸憂文王則患在羑里禍有靡測是以徬徨不安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='936:962'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-3a' );" name="001-3a" class="pb">[001-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='962:984'>　永懐無已耳序乃謂求賢審官不幾侵公事已乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='984:1007'>樛木后妃逮下也何逮乎能以恩意接下使不自塞也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1007:1030'>　上之臨下志于威嚴則其情不通志于妬忌則其生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1030:1053'>　不遂能忠能恕上下泰然樂可知矣葛生山谷間附</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1053:1076'>　木而起長二三丈藟亦葛類又名巨苽本草所謂千</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1076:1099'>　歳藟也葛藟得託樛木以遂其生比庶妾因后妃而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1099:1116'>　進御所謂樂只福履則頌禱之詞耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1116:1139'>螽斯后妃子孫衆多也非也衆妾相安相樂之詞也螽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1139:1165'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-3b' );" name="001-3b" class="pb">[001-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1165:1188'>　類有五在爾雅此土螽也其種獨蕃秋冬之際千百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1188:1211'>　為羣飛集田野絶不相害非以股鳴者振振言其衆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1211:1220'>　盛非仁厚之謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1220:1243'>桃夭后妃之所致也非也后妃荅樛木也凡木美實者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1243:1266'>　未必美華即華美矣不能早實唯桃華豐豔三年以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1266:1289'>　上便能作實以比衆妾年少色好又宜子也大學傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1289:1312'>　曰宜其家人而後可以教國人非君夫人能教國乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1312:1335'>兔罝后妃之化也非也文王之化也文治于岐四方無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1335:1361'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-4a' );" name="001-4a" class="pb">[001-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1361:1384'>　侮寢甲止戈武夫無所效其用相與優㳺田野從事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1384:1407'>　罝罔以銷磨其壯心焉曰干城曰好仇曰腹心計其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1407:1430'>　才也以此才而野處若深惜之實為國家治平喜矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1430:1453'>　兔道為迒往來有常所謂中逵自是兔迒非九達之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1453:1458'>　逵也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1458:1481'>芣苢后妃之美也非也周民室家樂完聚也無征戍則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1481:1504'>　民安其業室家無復離析死亡之憂所當恤者産難</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1504:1527'>　而已采芣苢宜産也治平之象溢於言表矣此其所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1527:1553'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-4b' );" name="001-4b" class="pb">[001-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1553:1560'>　以為風乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1560:1583'>漢廣徳廣所及也孰及之文徳及之也岐周處西北而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1583:1606'>　江漢實在其南文徳被乎南國南國之君思欲奉戴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1606:1629'>　猶畏紂之暴虐有不敢先賦此以見志曰喬木曰㳺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1629:1652'>　女喻文徳之可歆豔非犯禮妄求之説也錯薪也楚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1652:1675'>　也蔞也皆可刈之物也以錯薪翹翹秀起姑欲待其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1675:1698'>　黄落但刈楚及蔞而已喻惜名分不欲先去紂也孰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1698:1716'>　能先我歸周我當秣其馬而從其後矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1716:1742'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-5a' );" name="001-5a" class="pb">[001-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1742:1765'>汝墳道化行也曷行之行東諸侯也東諸侯服文徳而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1765:1788'>　朝周者必由汝墳而西故遵汝墳者往見伐其條枚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1788:1811'>　今則伐其條肄計已經年而始一來感其聘問之曠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1811:1834'>　也既見君子不以曠而棄我又私喜矣唯是王室虐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1834:1858'>　𦦨如燬不遑寧息故有曠也敢貳心哉文王三分天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1858:1881'>　下有二於漢廣汝墳而見之言婦人能閔君子者何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1881:1911'>　足以語此楚人謂火曰燥吳人曰<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1754' title='KR1754' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1754.png'/>齊人曰燬此稱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1911:1930'>　王室如燬則齊語矣故知為東諸侯之詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1930:1956'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-5b' );" name="001-5b" class="pb">[001-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1956:1979'>麟之趾闗雎之應也曷應之成王業者應之也周南闗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1979:2002'>　雎以至桃夭家之齊兔罝芣苢國之治漢廣汝墳則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2002:2025'>　天下其將平矣然而大統未集文王即世向非武王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2025:2048'>　周公繼述厥志王業何由而成乎麟神物也世不槩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2048:2071'>　有以比公子公孫不世出之賢聖耳曰子曰孫曰族</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2071:2084'>　舉皆賢聖非一故稱振振</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2084:2088'>召南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2088:2111'>鵲巢夫人之徳也夫人始來于何見徳乎于其能將姪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2111:2137'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-6a' );" name="001-6a" class="pb">[001-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2137:2160'>　娣俱來也古者諸侯一娶九女二國媵之以姪娣是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2160:2183'>　嘗有挾忌心不與姪娣偕行者矣此夫人獨能將之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2183:2206'>　故作者樂歌其事焉鵲工為巢綢繆鞏固喻君夫人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2206:2229'>　有國有家鳩拙於巢或託鵲巢而乳子則姪娣自喻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2229:2249'>　也傳謂鳲鳩均壹之徳以比夫人殆不然哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2249:2272'>采蘩夫人不失職也何以不失職祀以其時也祭有禴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2272:2295'>　有烝烝以進品物禴以薦新味南國歳味莫先于蘩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2295:2318'>　孟春芽始數寸香脆可珍碧葉白㲨故謂皤蒿物雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2318:2344'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-6b' );" name="001-6b" class="pb">[001-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2344:2367'>　微而敬薦之可謂能修常事矣被者祭服之通名少</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2367:2390'>　牢饋食主婦被裼衣侈袂薦自東房是其事也傳以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2390:2407'>　被為首飾箋又改被為髲何其鑿邪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2407:2430'>草蟲大夫妻能以禮自防也夫婦一體也逺離之久感</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2430:2453'>　時相念情之正也何必謂其以禮自防乎草蟲者蜻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2453:2476'>　蛚寒螿之總名張衡所謂大火流草蟲鳴是已阜螽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2476:2499'>　即周南所謂螽斯也草蟲喓喓阜螽趯趯深秋候也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2499:2522'>　采薇采蕨季春候也秋暮而往春暮未還道里悠逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2522:2548'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-7a' );" name="001-7a" class="pb">[001-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2548:2569'>　吉㐫莫卜是以用憂豈感物而興男女之思乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2569:2592'>采蘋大夫妻能循法度也何循乎法度善其能教女也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2592:2615'>　昏義古者婦人先嫁三月教之公宫祖廟已毁教之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2615:2638'>　于宗室教以婦徳婦言婦容婦功教成祭之牲用魚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2638:2661'>　芼用蘋藻所以成婦順也此采蘋藻以芼魚也奠于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2661:2684'>　宗室牖下教成之祭也不舉其物而舉所芼貴躬采</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2684:2698'>　也曰季女大夫之妻之女也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2698:2721'>甘棠美召伯也何美乎為其分陜能奉王政以正諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2721:2747'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-7b' );" name="001-7b" class="pb">[001-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2747:2770'>　使強不陵弱衆不暴寡江漢之間附庸小國實賴之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2770:2793'>　以安焉故託喻甘棠蔽芾之及物以志感豈聽訟棠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2793:2800'>　下之説乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2800:2823'>行露召伯聽訟也此非也嫠婦執節不貳之詞也唯野</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2823:2846'>　田草萊之區乃多行露唯鰥夫嫠婦乃有速獄之婚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2846:2869'>　録是詩者明露屋草茅習俗亦美也多露沾濡之可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2869:2892'>　厭我常夙夜謂其可厭矣喻潔已之有素也雀無角</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2892:2915'>　而穿屋鼠無牙而穿墉猶我未嘗許嫁妄致我于獄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2915:2941'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-8a' );" name="001-8a" class="pb">[001-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2941:2946'>　訟耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2946:2969'>羔羊鵲巢功致也此序非也南國大夫能節儉也諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2969:2992'>　狐裘大夫羔裘士羊裘制也此宜羔裘而羊裘以是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2992:3015'>　知其能儉服羊裘而委蛇自適無不足之色以是知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3015:3038'>　其能節古者五羊而成一裘百里大夫五羖見稱即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3038:3061'>　其事矣紽緎皆五知其皮之五也羔裘之直敵數羊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3061:3073'>　裘以尚節儉故寧羊裘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3073:3096'>殷其雷勸以義也此士妻之詞也按周制大行人司儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3096:3122'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-8b' );" name="001-8b" class="pb">[001-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3122:3145'>　上士八人中士十六人下士三十二人小雅偕偕士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3145:3168'>　子朝夕從事是已曰振振者衆詞也從者非一我所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3168:3191'>　懐之人可少休矣何為獨勞王事乎雷無形象猶有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3191:3214'>　聲響可求不在山南則在山北君子行役顧不知所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3214:3223'>　向往盖傷之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3223:3246'>摽有梅男女之及時也非實男女也處士樂及明時效</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3246:3269'>　用也月令孟夏賛桀俊遂賢良行爵出禄必當其位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3269:3292'>　故徴聘之典行焉梅實隕落正其候矣此時束帛之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3292:3318'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-9a' );" name="001-9a" class="pb">[001-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3318:3338'>　典不及必且後時矣故託士女相求以明志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3338:3368'>小星惠及下也非及下也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0591' title='KR0591' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0591.png'/>御入直居寢之詞也古者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3368:3391'>　王公臨事則有瞽史之道居寢則有暬御之箴莫非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3391:3414'>　賢也賢者在事故能安命而述職言列宿在天小大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3414:3437'>　異象王臣從政貴賤有等才有賢否位有崇卑各盡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3437:3460'>　其職而已參昴以喻大臣小星則自擬也列星之中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3460:3483'>　唯北斗參昴最為著見夏小正於參昴之伏見也屢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3483:3506'>　書之入直者因所見而興詞唯其入直居寢是以抱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3506:3532'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-9b' );" name="001-9b" class="pb">[001-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3532:3546'>　衾與裯豈賤妾進御之謂乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3546:3569'>江有汜美媵也何美乎以其不克與嫡偕行能待命於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3569:3592'>　國無貳志也水已決去而復入者為汜岐流為渚别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3592:3615'>　出為沱汜也渚也沱也媵自喻也言江水同源尚然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3615:3638'>　有汜有渚有沱我自它國來媵寧能必其與嫡夫人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3638:3660'>　偕往乎不怨不以而猶望其悔悟之萌可謂厚矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3660:3683'>野有死麕惡無禮也非無禮也嘉其亦猶行古之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3683:3706'>　上古昏嫁以麗皮為禮此以白茅包束麕鹿則麗皮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3706:3733'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-10a' );" name="001-10a" class="pb">[001-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3733:3756'>　之遺俗也誘之云者麗皮導其來聘之禮也稱尨吠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3756:3779'>　知為山谷野鄙之氓也士以茅束麗皮而來女則施</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3779:3802'>　衿結縭而往畧繁禮尚真淳宛然羲皇上世之風矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3802:3825'>　二南之詩有美而無刺其述風化事行往往在乎景</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3825:3848'>　象之間不因言語文字而盡之學詩者所當知焉俗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3848:3871'>　儒不通斯㫖至謂此詩為淫奔而欲刪之如其愚如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3871:3876'>　其愚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3876:3899'>何彼穠矣美王姬也非美王姬也美武王之能以女下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3899:3926'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-10b' );" name="001-10b" class="pb">[001-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3926:3949'>　嫁于齊也唐棣之華翩其反而語其能下降也故以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3949:3972'>　興王姬之肅雝焉桃李異色同時並盛故以興王姬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3972:3995'>　齊子兩貴之相當絲綸皆釣具絲以取小魚綸以致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3995:4018'>　大魚各有宜也唯齊侯之子乃足上當平王之孫耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='4018:4041'>　始周公未定諡法之時於文考或稱平王或稱寧王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='4041:4064'>　毛傳釋平王為文王是矣彼平王宜臼齊侯諸兒烏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4064:4087'>　足以汚召南邪王姬適齊實昉乎此帝乙歸妹之例</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4087:4095'>　也故謹存之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4095:4122'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-11a' );" name="001-11a" class="pb">[001-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4122:4145'>騶虞鵲巢之應也非應鵲巢也記仁愛之及庶物也古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4145:4168'>　者春獀夏苗秋獮冬狩一以除田害一以講武事葭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4168:4191'>　蓬之茁則春獀矣葭蓬記其時豝豵之五記其物一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4191:4214'>　發而罷記其仁騶也虞也記其官吁嗟乎者隠痛之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4214:4237'>　詞也呼騶虞所以止殺也天子不合圍諸侯不揜羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4237:4260'>　五豝而取一焉明不揜羣也六騶羣騶事在左傳山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4260:4283'>　虞澤虞屬在地官七騶咸駕著之月令騶虞之為官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4283:4306'>　也顯矣而毛傳遽為白虎黒文之説夫白虎黒文爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4306:4333'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0038', 'WYG', '001-11b' );" name="001-11b" class="pb">[001-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4333:4346'>　雅釋獸所不載豈其然乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4346:4349'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4349:4352'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4352:4355'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4355:4358'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4358:4361'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4361:4364'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4364:4371'>　詩故卷一</span><br/>
